09 in video gaming|2009]]\n|Game of the Year\n|''[[Batman: Arkham Asylum]]''\n|''[[Call of Duty: Modern Warfare 2]]'' (Todd Alderman, Steve Fukuda, Mackey McCandlish, Zied Rieke)<br />''[[Uncharted 2: Among Thieves]]'' (Richard Lemarchand, [[Neil Druckmann]])\n|[[Sefton Hill]]\n|[[Rocksteady Studios]]\n|-\n|[[2010 in video gaming|2010]]\n|Game of the Year\n|''[[Red Dead Redemption]]''\n|''[[Assassin's Creed: Brotherhood]]'' (Steven Masters)<br />''[[Darksiders]]'' (Timothy Bell)<br />''[[Heavy Rain]]'' ([[David Cage]])<br />''[[Limbo (video game)|Limbo]]'' (Arnt Jensen)<br />''[[Mass Effect 2]]'' ([[Casey Hudson]])<br />''[[StarCraft II: Wings of Liberty]]'' (Robert Pardo)\n|Steve Martin, David Kunkler\n|[[Rockstar San Diego]]\n|-\n|[[2011 in video gaming|2011]]\n|Game of the Year\n|''[[Minecraft]]''\n|''[[Batman: Arkham City]]'' (Daniel Bailie, Nathan Burlow)<br />''[[Battlefield 3]]'' (Patrick Bach)<br />''[[Catherine (video game)|Catherine]]'' (Kazuhisa Wada)<br />''[[Dark Souls]]'' (Hidetaka Miyazaki)<br />''[[The Elder Scrolls V: Skyrim]]'' (Bruce Nesmith)<br />''[[Portal 2]]''<br />''[[Uncharted 3: Drake's Deception]]'' (Richard Lemarchand, Jacob Minkoff)\n|[[Markus Persson]]\n|[[Mojang]]\n|-\n|[[2012 in video gaming|2012]]\n|Game of the Year\n|''[[Journey (2012 video game)|Journey]]''\n|''[[Borderlands 2]]''<br />''[[Far Cry 3]]'' (Kevin Guillemette, Jamie Keen, Andrea Zanini)<br />''[[Spec Ops: The Line]]'' (Cory Davis, Fran\u00e7ois Coulon)<br />''[[The Walking Dead (video game)|The Walking Dead]]'' ([[Sean Vanaman]])<br />''[[Torchlight II]]''\n|[[Jenova Chen]], [[Robin Hunicke]]\n|[[thatgamecompany]]\n|-\n|[[2013 in video gaming|2013]]\n|Game of the Year\n|''[[The Last of Us]]''\n|''[[Battlefield 4]]'' (Lars Gustavsson)<br />''[[Bioshock: Infinite]]'' ([[Ken Levine (game developer)|Ken Levine]])<br />''[[Grand Theft Auto V]]'' ([[Leslie Benzies]], Imran Sarwar)<br />''[[Super Mario 3D World]]''<br />''[[The Legend of Zelda: A Link Between Worlds]]'' ([[Ei